summary: This mod adds a cursed house near dragon bridge
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a cursed house near dragon bridge, the exact location is indicated on a picture. The mod is similar to Dead manor one altough i didn\'t copy the idea, as i started to plan this mod before the other one got relased.
There\'s a small background story to explain what has happened in the house, and you\'ll gain a reward at the end of the adventure. I hope you\'ll like it and you won\'t find bugs, and please excuse me for my bad english!
author: DOC
